[Episode 12]

3
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:15,620
Why must you do this?

4
00:00:22,780 --> 00:00:24,860
Naturally,
it's because I am fond of him.

5
00:00:43,980 --> 00:00:45,740
Then what about your promise to me?

6
00:00:48,020 --> 00:00:49,020
I've forgotten about it.

7
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:00,820
Second Young Master.

8
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:02,660
Second Young Master.

9
00:01:03,740 --> 00:01:04,500
Pei Jingheng.

10
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:07,430
♪I recite a verse of Water Melody♪

11
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:10,500
I knew you'd come to save me.

12
00:01:11,580 --> 00:01:12,180
It's all right now.

13
00:01:12,180 --> 00:01:14,180
♪I stand beneath the phoenix tree♪

14
00:01:14,420 --> 00:01:17,540
♪Waiting for you to turn back
and look at me♪

15
00:01:18,460 --> 00:01:21,380
♪If I could hold your hand in this life♪

16
00:01:21,940 --> 00:01:24,940
♪I would no longer fear the years ahead♪

17
00:01:25,380 --> 00:01:28,140
♪I only wish
the gentle breeze would remain♪

18
00:01:28,540 --> 00:01:31,940
♪And that we may stay together
till the end♪

19
00:01:32,220 --> 00:01:35,340
♪Everything fades,
yet tenderness remains♪

20
00:01:35,820 --> 00:01:38,780
♪The autumn wind
carries my longing for you♪

21
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:42,180
♪I sigh,
for life is but a fleeting dream♪

22
00:01:42,420 --> 00:01:45,580
♪And I have no one accompanying me now♪

23
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:49,300
♪I look up at pear blossoms
drifting down♪

24
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:52,820
♪Who is it bearing all this pain alone?♪

25
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:55,900
♪I look back suddenly♪

26
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:59,790
♪Only to see your brows knit with worry♪

27
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:03,210
♪It's easy to see
the trees upon the hills♪

28
00:02:03,210 --> 00:02:04,380
♪And branches on the trees♪

29
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:07,900
♪Yet so hard for you to see my heart♪

30
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:13,860
♪Perhaps we missed too much
in a past life♪

31
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:18,300
♪The autumn moon shines bright,
and countless poems are written for it♪

32
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:22,020
♪Yet none of them matter
as long as I can stay by your side♪

33
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:27,660
♪Across mountains and seas,
I will meet you again within my dreams♪

